previewTitle: The biggest online incubator and accelerator. Provides work per equity and helps in raising capital from a large network of angel investors and VCs. - FasterCapital
preview: FasterCapital is a global online incubator and accelerator that helps startups in raising capital and offers technical and business development services. In our Tech Cofounder program, we will become your technical cofounder or technical partner and develop the whole product from A to Z. FasterCapital provides also business development per equity in Grow your Startup program including growth hacks, entering new markets, increasing sales, finding new customers, and others. FasterCapital will invest also 50% of the money needed per equity. We will help you also in raising the capital and connecting you to 100,000 investors
